title: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Railways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Railways, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and shows the locations of the Railway infrastructure in the Sachsen-Anhalt administrative area in the country of Germany. Railways include trams, subways, and standard trains. This railway data set was uploaded as a poly line shape file and includes attribute information for Feature name and feature type.
